description:
Tune Your Guitar Pro v2 is finally available! Sporting an all new interface, the premium version of the Hot Apps winner is still the best guitar tuner for webOS!

Tune Your Guitar plays the notes and you tune your strings to the proper sound. Choose from 11 different tunings:
Standard
Dropped D
Down 1/2 Step
Up 1/2 Step
Dropped C
Open A
Open C
Open D
Open G
Open E
Pentatonic

The app saves the last tuning you picked, so it matches your guitar every time.

Please rate the app and leave comments. You can also e-mail me directly to get help & offer suggestions by tapping "Help" on the menu screen.
versionNote: All-new interface, speed increase, more reliable
